  },
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "titleStrip",
        "attrs": {
          "removable": true
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Last Light"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "body",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "attrs": {
              "level": 2
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Logline"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "On the morning of her grandmother's death, a young woman returns to her childhood home in search of one final memory."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "attrs": {
              "level": 2
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Characters"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "NALI — 28, the granddaughter. Tired eyes, steady hands."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "BABAN — 84, the grandmother. Frail but lucid; a lifetime in every breath."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "DR. HASSAN — 60s, the family doctor. Calm, patient, has seen this many times."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "type": "scene",
            "attrs": {
              "id": "scene-001",
              "notes": "Open quiet. Mist as a character.",
              "revisionFlag": null,
              "metadata": {
                "linkedScenes": [],
                "references": [],
                "production": {}
              }
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "sceneHeading",
                "attrs": {
                  "setting": "EXT.",
                  "time": "DAWN",
                  "headingStyle": null
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "OLD HOUSE — ROSE GARDEN"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "A beat-up car rolls to a stop at the end of a long gravel drive. The "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "engine"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "underline"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "ticks"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " as it "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "italic"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "cools"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ". Mist drifts low through an overgrown rose garden."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "NALI (28) steps out, holding a thin coat against the cold. She looks at the house — and the house looks back."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "She does not move. The wind moves for her, lifting a single white petal across her shoe."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "transition",
                "attrs": {
                  "presetType": "CUT"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "CUT"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "scene",
            "attrs": {
              "id": "scene-002",
              "notes": "Hold on hands meeting. Two generations.",
              "revisionFlag": null,
              "metadata": {
                "linkedScenes": [],
                "references": [],
                "production": {}
              }
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "sceneHeading",
                "attrs": {
                  "setting": "EXT.",
                  "time": "CONTINUOUS",
                  "headingStyle": null
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "BABAN'S BEDROOM"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "BABAN lies under an embroidered quilt. Sunlight pools on the floor. NALI kneels at the bedside, her hand finding her grandmother's. This is adding to the script not to the body."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "character",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "tag",
                        "attrs": {
                          "tagType": "character",
                          "entityId": "47a05ccf-a967-4d5c-9f65-aa62f2542158"
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "BABAN"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "parenthetical",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "(barely a whisper)"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "You came."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "character",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "tag",
                        "attrs": {
                          "tagType": "character",
                          "entityId": "15201fa6-09cf-4786-a384-3c0bbd973dd8"
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "NALI"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I always do."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "A long silence. "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "tag",
                        "attrs": {
                          "tagType": "character",
                          "entityId": "e578a64f-e6d2-4d69-97ba-1771805b974d"
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Baban"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "'s eyes drift to the window — to a tree neither of them has "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "annotation",
                        "attrs": {
                          "id": "c7e36f96-3770-4668-90b8-9fd25b69dc73",
                          "text": "in months not years or days",
                          "color": "#FFE08A",
                          "createdAt": "2026-05-16T11:40:40.432Z",
                          "author": null,
                          "status": "resolved"
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "spoken about in years"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "transition",
                "attrs": {
                  "presetType": "CUT"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "CUT"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "scene",
            "attrs": {
              "id": "scene-003",
              "notes": "The photograph turn — pivot of the film.",
              "revisionFlag": null,
              "metadata": {
                "linkedScenes": [],
                "references": [],
                "production": {}
              }
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "sceneHeading",
                "attrs": {
                  "setting": "INT.",
                  "time": "DAY",
                  "headingStyle": null
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "KITCHEN"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Steam rises from a kettle. "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "tag",
                        "attrs": {
                          "tagType": "character",
                          "entityId": "ent-nali"
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "NALI"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " moves like a guest in her own childhood, opening the wrong drawers. She finds a small tin box behind the sugar jar."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Inside: a single black-and-white photograph. A girl, ten years old, standing by a lake. Nali stares at it. She doesn't remember the lake. She doesn't remember being the girl."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "tag",
                        "attrs": {
                          "tagType": "character",
                          "entityId": "ent-hassan"
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "DR. HASSAN"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " (60s) steps into the doorway, leather bag in hand. He has watched many families do this."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "character",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "DR. HASSAN"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "She doesn't have long."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "character",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "NALI"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "parenthetical",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "(not looking up)"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "She doesn't need long. She needs me."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "She slides the photograph into her coat pocket."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "transition",
                "attrs": {
                  "presetType": "CUT"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "CUT"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "scene",
            "attrs": {
              "id": "scene-004",
              "notes": "The promise. Soft light only.",
              "revisionFlag": null,
              "metadata": {
                "linkedScenes": [],
                "references": [],
                "production": {}
              }
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "sceneHeading",
                "attrs": {
                  "setting": "INT.",
                  "time": "DUSK",
                  "headingStyle": null
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "BABAN'S BEDROOM"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The room is gold and shadow. Baban's breathing is shallow. Nali holds the photograph between them so they can both see it."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "character",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "BABAN"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "You were happy there. We both were. I couldn't tell you why we stopped going."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "character",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "NALI"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Tell me now."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "character",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "BABAN"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "parenthetical",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "(a small smile)"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I'm too tired for the long answer. Just — promise me you'll go back to the lake."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "character",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "NALI"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I promise."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Baban's hand goes still. Nali doesn't cry. Not yet."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "transition",
                "attrs": {
                  "presetType": "DISSOLVE"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "DISSOLVE"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "scene",
            "attrs": {
              "id": "scene-005",
              "notes": "End on motion forward — never backward.",
              "revisionFlag": null,
              "metadata": {
                "linkedScenes": [],
                "references": [],
                "production": {}
              }
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "sceneHeading",
                "attrs": {
                  "setting": "EXT.",
                  "time": "NIGHT",
                  "headingStyle": null
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "OLD HOUSE — DRIVEWAY"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "tag",
                        "attrs": {
                          "tagType": "character",
                          "entityId": "ent-nali"
                        }
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "NALI"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " walks back to the car. The photograph is in her hand, not her pocket. Behind her, one lit window in the house goes dark."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "She gets in. Looks at the photo on the steering wheel. Starts the engine."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "shot",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "TAIL LIGHTS RECEDE"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "action",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Down the long drive, into the road, into the morning that is becoming."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "transition",
                "attrs": {
                  "presetType": "FADE OUT"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "FADE OUT"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
